    "summary": "The user asks a series of questions regarding the viability and equity of congestion pricing in urban planning. While the assistant begins with a balanced overview, it progressively adopts an authoritative, pro-congestion pricing stance, dismissing economic concerns as obstacles to be managed rather than valid counter-arguments.",
